\v 23 For {it is} finished and decreed: the Lord Yahweh of hosts is about to carry {it} out throughout all the land.

\p
\v 24 Therefore, thus says the Lord Yahweh of hosts, “My people who live {in} Zion, do not fear the Assyrian. He will strike you with the rod and raise his staff against you in the way of Egypt
\v 25 for just a very little {time}; then the fury and my nose will end on account of their destruction.”

\p
